'''Ynara Yinnivan''' was a member of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic's]] [[Astrographic Survey Institute]].

[[Astrography|Astrographer]] Yinnivan compiled the Institute's report on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Thanta Zilbra (planet)|Thanta Zilbra]].

